  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Enjoy a buffet breakfast on the terrace and tuck into a choice of freshly baked cakes, pastries and breads along with cheeses and cold cuts. For half board guests, dinner is served in the hotel restaurant with a view of the lake, you can enjoy four courses from the à la carte menu.<span style="text-decoration: underline;"></span></p>
<p>A snack bar is located on the veranda by the pool and offers small plates during the day and the hotel's bar has an impressive cocktail and wine list as well as a lovely terrace.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
