  <description><![CDATA[<p>The service at the Hotel Maximilian is great and nothing is too much trouble for the staff. The centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/89a5238595c34e53a5ef4c989b459fce" href="/{localLink:umb://document/89a5238595c34e53a5ef4c989b459fce}" title="Malcesine">Malcesine</a> is about a 20-minute walk away along the lakeside promenade or you can borrow a bike from the hotel and cycle there.</p>
<h2>Lakeside location in Malcesine</h2>
<p>Located in the beautiful bay of Val di Sogno (Dream Valley), which is a protected area on the lakefront surrounded by greenery, Hotel Maximilian's the ideal place for a relaxing lakeside retreat. We love the restaurant where you can have dinner outside on the terrace next to the lake. In the colourful gardens, you'll find a large swimming pool and whirlpool with unrivalled views of the bay and mountains beyond.</p>
<h2>Relaxing spa facilities</h2>
<p>The wellness centre offers a range of facilities including a Turkish bath and sauna as well as beauty treatments and massages that can all be booked and paid for locally. It's the ideal way to finish off a leisurely stroll along the lakeside path.</p>]]></description>
