  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Garden View Rooms </strong>are located in the main building on the ground floor and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed). They have a terrace and garden views.</p>
<p><strong>Lake View Rooms </strong>are located in the main building on the ground floor and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed). They have a terrace and lovely views of the lake.</p>
<p><strong>Villa Stefania Suites</strong> sleep up to three people and are located in the annexe (extra bed is a double sofa bed). They have a balcony or terrace and lake views. These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Lake View Rooms for Sole Use</strong> are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p>Please specify twin or double beds at the time of booking.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Shower</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Air-conditioning</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p>Cots are available on request.</p>
<p><strong>Local fees &amp; taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tax of approx. €2 per person per night is payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
